      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled, preserving its flawless original paint which retains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets remain pristine under factory mats, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a documented history of exhaustive preventative maintenance and low, gentle miles. From the spotless engine bay to the unblemished alloy wheels wrapped in fresh rubber, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey example of automotive excellence, complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service binder.",
